OL,7,FA NHS trust has dropped misconduct and
OL,8,Fbullying allegations against an
OL,9,Femergency department nurse who
OL,10,Fcomplained about having to use a
OL,11,Fchanging room with a transgender
OL,12,Fdoctor, following a UK Supreme Court
OL,13,Fruling on gender.
OL,15,FNurse Sandie Peggie was suspended from
OL,16,FVictoria Hospital in Fife, Scotland in
OL,17,FJanuary last year after a transgender
OL,18,Fmedic, Dr Beth Upton, made allegations
OL,19,Fof bullying and harassment towards Ms
OL,20,FPeggie.
