OL,7,FMs Peggie was stood down while the
OL,8,Fhospital board considered four gross
OL,9,Fmisconduct allegations against her,
OL,10,Fincluding one of misgendering the
OL,11,Fdoctor and over an encounter with the
OL,12,Fdoctor in the female-only changing
OL,13,Froom.
OL,15,FDr Upton also cited concerns about
OL,16,F"patient care".
