OL,7,FMs Peggie's lawyer, Margaret Gribbon,
OL,8,Fsaid the night before the tribunal was
OL,9,Fdue to recommence hearings, the Fife
OL,10,Fhealth board decided not to uphold the
OL,11,Fmisconduct allegations towards her
OL,12,Fclient.
OL,14,F"Sandie is relieved and delighted that
OL,15,Fthis 18-month-long internal process
OL,16,Fhas concluded and cleared her of all
OL,17,Fallegations," she said.
OL,19,FNHS Fife confirmed it had concluded
OL,20,Fits internal investigation into the
OL,21,Fnurse's conduct.
