OL,7,F"It considered several allegations,
OL,8,Fincluding regarding interactions
OL,9,Fbetween colleagues and patient care,"
OL,10,Fthe health board said.
OL,12,F"After reviewing the evidence
OL,13,Fpresented, including written
OL,14,Fsubmissions and witness testimony, the
OL,15,Fpanel found that there was
OL,16,Finsufficient evidence to support a
OL,17,Ffinding of misconduct.
